---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>FRDVC</h1>
      <p class="tagline">
        探索价值（Value）、欲望（Desire）、承认（Recognition）、成本（Cost）与流动（Flow）之间的动态关系
      </p>
      <p class="subtitle">
        一个持续发展的跨学科研究项目，通过理论、工程实现与实验观察，不断修正和完善对复杂现象的理解。
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>核心命题</h2>
      <div class="questions">
        <div class="question-item">
          <span class="q-marker"></span>
          <p>个体行为如何形成群体结构？</p>
        </div>
        <div class="question-item">
          <span class="q-marker"></span>
          <p>市场、组织与社会秩序如何从局部规则中涌现？</p>
        </div>
        <div class="question-item">
          <span class="q-marker"></span>
          <p>流动机制如何塑造价值与差异？</p>
        </div>
        <div class="question-item">
          <span class="q-marker"></span>
          <p>简单规则是否能够生成复杂系统？</p>
        </div>
        <div class="question-item">
          <span class="q-marker"></span>
          <p>如何通过计算模拟验证理论假设？</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>研究方向</h2>
      <div class="directions">
        <span class="tag">复杂系统</span>
        <span class="tag">涌现</span>
        <span class="tag">多智能体系统</span>
        <span class="tag">网络科学</span>
        <span class="tag">行为经济学</span>
        <span class="tag">计算社会科学</span>
        <span class="tag">人工智能</span>
        <span class="tag">科学哲学与技术哲学</span>
        <span class="tag">信息流动与价值形成</span>
        <span class="tag">决策机制与反馈系统</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>研究方法</h2>
      <div class="method-flow">
        <div class="method-step">
          <span class="step-num">1</span>
          <strong>提出问题</strong>
        </div>
        <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="method-step">
          <span class="step-num">2</span>
          <strong>建立模型</strong>
        </div>
        <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="method-step">
          <span class="step-num">3</span>
          <strong>工程实现</strong>
        </div>
        <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="method-step">
          <span class="step-num">4</span>
          <strong>实验观察</strong>
        </div>
        <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="method-step">
          <span class="step-num">5</span>
          <strong>修正模型</strong>
        </div>
        <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span>
        <div class="method-step">
          <span class="step-num">∞</span>
          <strong>持续迭代</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="method-note">理论不是终点，而是实验的起点。每一次实验，无论成功或失败，都将作为模型演化的重要依据。</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>当前项目</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h3>FRDVC Framework</h3>
          <p>探索复杂系统中价值生成与行为演化机制的核心理论框架。研究价值、欲望、承认、成本与流动的动态关系。</p>
          <span class="status">持续研究中</span>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Agent Lab</h3>
          <p>多智能体模拟平台。通过设计简单规则，观察合作、竞争、资源流动、网络形成以及系统演化等现象。</p>
          <span class="status">开发中</span>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3>Research Log</h3>
          <p>公开记录研究过程：理论推演、实验记录、模型修订、阅读笔记、阶段性总结。完整保留从概念到实践的演化轨迹。</p>
          <span class="status">持续更新</span>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>研究理念</h2>
      <blockquote class="motto">
        研究目标并非建立封闭的理论体系，而是通过理论、工程实现与实验观察，不断修正和完善对复杂现象的理解。
      </blockquote>
      <p class="focus-statement">
        关注复杂系统中结构如何生成，以及个体行为如何通过反馈、选择与流动机制逐渐演化为宏观秩序。
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 24px 80px;
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 0 48px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: #374151;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 12px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #6b7280;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .section {
    margin-top: 56px;
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
  }

  .questions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .question-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    background: #f9fafb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 3px solid #6366f1;
  }

  .q-marker {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #6366f1;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .question-item p {
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .directions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    background: #eef2ff;
    color: #4338ca;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .method-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .method-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    background: #f3f4f6;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .step-num {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background: #6366f1;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .method-step strong {
    color: #111827;
  }

  .arrow {
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .method-note {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .card {
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .card h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }

  .card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }

  .status {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    background: #fef3c7;
    color: #92400e;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .motto {
    border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    background: #fafafe;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #374151;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .focus-statement {
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 40px 0 32px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    .method-flow {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .arrow {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>